[normal]. Some of the examples of engineering mistakes given by Scott Adams are 
[normal]Hidenberg
[normal], Space Shuttle
[normal] Challenger
[normal], Hubble space telescope, Apollo 13, Titanic, Ford Pinto, and 
[normal]Corvair
